    <Paragraph Type="Character"><Text>DEV</Text></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action"><Text>That sound fake.</Text></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character"><Text>RICO</Text></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action"><Text>It is not fake.</Text></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action"><Text>Malik says nothing.</Text></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action"><Text>But he hears all of it.</Text></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action"><Text>The dashboard glows in the dark. The map reroutes.</Text></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character"><Text>NEW STOP ADDED.</Text></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action"><Text>Malik sees it immediately. His grip on the wheel tightens just a little.</Text></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action"><Text>Rachel finally looks up long enough to notice that he noticed. Then she looks back down.</Text></Paragraph>
