    <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading"><Text>INT. MALIK'S SUV – MOVING – NIGHT</Text></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action"><Text>The city slides by in layers.</Text></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action"><Text>Neon signs flicker past.</Text></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action"><Text>A train rattles somewhere above them.</Text></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action"><Text>A dog barks from a dark yard.</Text></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action"><Text>The music shifts slightly as the next track fades in. Malik adjusts the mirror again.</Text></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action"><Text>Still the same four people behind him.</Text></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action"><Text>Still the same unanswered questions.</Text></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action"><Text>He keeps driving.</Text></Paragraph>
