    <Paragraph Type="Action"><Text>A stop on the app becomes strategy.</Text></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action"><Text>He knows he might be wrong.</Text></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action"><Text>But he also knows nights like this sometimes turn into stories people tell later.</Text></Paragraph>
